Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not falling for that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Ulquiorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:24.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what you wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Hollowfication!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:29.13,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:29.13,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:31.08,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:31.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.31,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.31,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.02,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.02,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:37.13,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:37.13,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:39.08,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi mo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:39.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.71,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.71,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.15,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tanoshii uragiri ni atte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.15,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, betrayal can be pleasurable...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.45,J,,0000,0000,0000,,torawarenai atashi ga koko ni iru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.45,E,,0000,0000,0000,,But I stand right here - not giving in to temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.84,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tarinai tsukinai nandatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.84,E,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enough," "not enough," whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:57.94,J,,0000,0000,0000,,motto hizumasete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:57.94,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.80,J,,0000,0000,0000,,pataan kashita konna sekai ja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.80,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Living in this routine-laden world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:04.82,J,,0000,0000,0000,,jibun ga dare nano ka wakaranakunaru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:04.82,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...is enough to make you forget who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:08.01,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be stereotyped...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:08.01,J,,0000,0000,0000,,waku ni hamaritakunai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:12.14,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kimetsukenaide yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:12.14,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...so don't make assumptions about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:15.90,J,,0000,0000,0000,,michi naki michi wo yuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:15.90,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to blaze my own trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:19.30,J,,0000,0000,0000,,soko ni itatte matteitatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:19.30,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will ever be accomplished...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.19,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nani mo hajimaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.19,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you just stand around waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:22.93,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:22.93,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:25.10,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:25.10,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.70,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.70,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:33.60,J,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no omoidoori ni wa sasenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:33.60,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:34.61,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:34.61,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:36.87,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:36.87,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:38.84,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi wo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:38.84,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:42.38,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:42.38,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.02,J,,0000,0000,0000,,anata no moto ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.02,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm past the point of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:48.07,J,,0000,0000,0000,,mou kaerenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:48.07,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot go back to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.00,J,,0000,0000,0000,,atashi wa atashirashiku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.00,E,,0000,0000,0000,,On my own terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.57,J,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.57,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wanna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Ulquiorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:09.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to kill\Nthis woman already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:35.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let yourself be distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:39.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on your own opponent, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this guy by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:06.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:13.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue-...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Asking questions\Nduring a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are easy-going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri Kurotsuchi treated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He treated Abarai first,\Nso I took longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:33.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, Sado and Kuchiki\Nare still in a battle right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you crawl out of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot you with all that power,\Nbut it didn't go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sturdier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many things in\Nthe way here, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, are you sure about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ulquiorra, I'm taking this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that concerned\Nfor that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a fool...\NComing here just to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were going to be late,\Nyou should've just run away instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind not saying things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:44.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like I got\Nhere late because I hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:53.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because a dubious scientist\Ntook his sweet time healing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:57.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then blame that "dubious scientist."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:00.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of him,\Nyou're going to die by my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:12.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that dubious scientist\Nquite enough without you telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard... You're making me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting sick of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The god-like power of my Arbol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:41.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To create an infinite number\Nof loyal soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of my Calaveras?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:06:00.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I, who was bestowed\Ncreator-like powers by Lord Aizen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,could not become an Espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:10.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is absurd for rodents such as\Nyourselves to defy the great Espada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,End your life here...Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:26.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not falling for that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quick when it\Ncomes to dodging!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems you're not\Neven quick at dodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How many would you\Nlike this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same no matter\Nhow many of these hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not worth dodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that level, it has no effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this woman the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:40.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the reason why you won't pull out\Nthat mask because this woman is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:47.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:50.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then pull out your mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurosaki isn't able to exert\N{\i1}his full Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:08.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he did, Inoue wouldn't be able\N{\i1}to withstand his Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:18.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like something\Nchanged a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:22.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't have time\Nto waste with you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the same\Nno matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you don't assume that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do the same thing every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike my previous attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that loosens your Reishi bonds and\Nmakes them easier to take away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes even\Nan Arrancar's Hierro penetrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me, small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the spirit to\Ncontinue to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,even against such\Na large number of soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:26.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, Soul Reaper,\Nyou have limitless energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this battle is also limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to be\Nyour endless opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pushed back by these numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't get near Rudobon,\N{\i1}the main entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:46.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, it'll just needlessly\N{\i1}deplete my stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:18.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked so chilled\Nand relaxed earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you're starting\Nto look stifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be pointed out\Nby the one who looks stifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't stop talking, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you meant\Nby stealing Reishi and whatnot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:43.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but that level of power\Nwon't do any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right about that Soul Reaper\Nbeing more interesting than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,after being saved by\Nthat scientist of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:00.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go badmouthing\Nthat scientist too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't want to regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! Where were you aiming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of options, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to die now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to being\Na slow learner,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you're right up there with Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:39.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I was just\Ntaking random aim at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aiming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was creating a field to lure you into.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my true aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:11.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:16.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume that I will do\Nthe same thing every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji...Sado...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:31.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NYou're sure taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:34.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the two of you?\NWhat happened to the ones below?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We took care of them, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already\Nan invincible team, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado must be quite annoyed\Nto have you as his confused partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:45.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to help you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:59.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,More people aren't going\Nto change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:04.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just send in enough soldiers\Nto match the three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:09.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He can increase the number\Nof soldiers infinitely, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:11.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like some kind of fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, fruits don't grow infinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They will if you keep\Nwatering them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:20.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Plants aren't such simple things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- They seem to be\N- For a big guy, you sure like to nitpick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:26.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- getting along better now...\N- What do you know about plants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How're we going fight him, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no limit to these numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you two to take care of\Nevery one of his soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine... Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,El Directo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:06.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I can't use Sprenger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:09.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,because it takes too much time\Nduring a one-on-one battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:13.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But because you played with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:15.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you weren't wary of anything,\Nand that helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:22.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...\NYou're really pushing your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:26.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still stand.\NYou are quite sturdy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful beyond that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That dubious scientist gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:41.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've laid mines especially\Ndesigned for Arrancars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a slow learner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I explain to you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:15:00.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that luring you into that field\Nwas my biggest aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't build that there by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:10.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the locations where\NI had set the mines,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and after gauging the distance\Nbetween us, built it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't move too much\Nfor your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Yammy,\Nwho Szayelaporro talked about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:25.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! So what of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that I felt sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't shown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you could've gone on\Na few more rampages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:44.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mala Suerte... I feel for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:52.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:56.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On my way here, I snapped\Na few pillars at each level,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll surely fall all the way\Nto the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida... Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like a ghost or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:14.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't, but...just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those explosions\Nyou heard were mines
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that Kurotsuchi had me bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They go off if their Spiritual Pressure\Nsensors detect
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,an Arrancar within range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I carved out the ceiling\Nof the level below
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:26.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and placed them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:31.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy, Yammy, never even\Ngave a second thought to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:36.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,my aim of driving him into\Nthe minefield, so he fell for my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other doubts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never doubted you from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You just went rambling on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an annoying guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If Inoue can't completely block\Nmy Spiritual Pressure with her Rikka,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to protect her with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to do that\Neven without you telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:11.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Ulquiorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what you wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Hollowfication!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:07.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How far does he intend to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:31.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we above Las Noches' ceiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh...This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Ulquiorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Ulquiorra has broken\Nthrough the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:21.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Two things are forbidden below\Nthe ceilings of Las Noches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:28.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is the Gran Rey Cero,\Na Cero that exists for an Espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other is the sword release\Nof an Espada
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that is ranked\Ncuatro and above.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because both\Nare so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:41.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that they would threaten\Nto destroy Las Noches itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Enclose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Murcielago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:43.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Extend your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let down your guard\Nfor a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You reflexively used Getsuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:23.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't done that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:31.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,your head would've been blown off\Nand rolling by my feet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:23.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado and I understand\Neach other completely now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:26.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell what I want to do\Neven if I don't say it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:34.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me it's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:38.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Illustrated Guide--\N- Today, I'll explain the Fifth Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:41.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no stairs\Nin the Fifth Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:42.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To reach the upper level,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:44.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you must either fly in from\Nthe outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or break through the ceiling\Nof the lower level to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:47.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:50.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling wall is thick,\Nwith many pillars,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and is well-made to\Nresist vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:54.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:55.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just hear me explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:58.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To get there, I broke pillars,\Ndug through the ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:00.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and set mines along the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:02.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the hell were you\Ndoing looking all ridiculous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:03.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shut up!
